  "detailed_description": "A game like you've never seen before, <strong>Morph Animals</strong> 👱‍♂️🐺🐴🐻🦄!<br><br><strong>Transform yourself</strong> into different animals to complete quests and explore the world.<br>Each animal has its unique abilities. Make sure to morph into the correct animal to complete your challenge 🪄!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2599150/extras/82628c8b6320cd4279aa8559bf06ec85.avif?t=1696545271\" width=428 height=140 /></span><br><br><strong>Defeat enemies</strong> around the world and become more powerful.<br>You can use different morphs for different enemies 🦄!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2599150/extras/43ca03738d3ba95bddd5fe8d39105d15.avif?t=1696545271\" width=428 height=140 /></span><br><br><strong>Complete quests</strong> to unlock MORE!<br>You can find quests around the map 🌍.<br>At the end of each quest, you will get some rewards 💰.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2599150/extras/483a863cb16fec49f19befedaaf827aa.avif?t=1696545271\" width=428 height=140 /></span><br><br><strong>Collect, buy, sell,</strong> or even <strong>CRAFT</strong> resources to fill your inventory.<br>The best way to get artifacts/ resources is by defeating enemies ⚔️.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2599150/extras/92b16fcfcb8d336ed2c014307159408f.avif?t=1696545271\" width=428 height=140 /></span><br><br><strong>Unveil the lore</strong> of Morph Animals.<br>Will you be able to complete and unveil the game's lore 👀?<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2599150/extras/53768b6c097bba3c8a15d5e4a32ec924.avif?t=1696545271\" width=428 height=140 /></span>",
  "about_the_game": "A game like you've never seen before, <strong>Morph Animals</strong> 👱‍♂️🐺🐴🐻🦄!<br><br><strong>Transform yourself</strong> into different animals to complete quests and explore the world.<br>Each animal has its unique abilities. Make sure to morph into the correct animal to complete your challenge 🪄!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2599150/extras/82628c8b6320cd4279aa8559bf06ec85.avif?t=1696545271\" width=428 height=140 /></span><br><br><strong>Defeat enemies</strong> around the world and become more powerful.<br>You can use different morphs for different enemies 🦄!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2599150/extras/43ca03738d3ba95bddd5fe8d39105d15.avif?t=1696545271\" width=428 height=140 /></span><br><br><strong>Complete quests</strong> to unlock MORE!<br>You can find quests around the map 🌍.<br>At the end of each quest, you will get some rewards 💰.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2599150/extras/483a863cb16fec49f19befedaaf827aa.avif?t=1696545271\" width=428 height=140 /></span><br><br><strong>Collect, buy, sell,</strong> or even <strong>CRAFT</strong> resources to fill your inventory.<br>The best way to get artifacts/ resources is by defeating enemies ⚔️.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2599150/extras/92b16fcfcb8d336ed2c014307159408f.avif?t=1696545271\" width=428 height=140 /></span><br><br><strong>Unveil the lore</strong> of Morph Animals.<br>Will you be able to complete and unveil the game's lore 👀?<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2599150/extras/53768b6c097bba3c8a15d5e4a32ec924.avif?t=1696545271\" width=428 height=140 /></span>",
